001package org.vafer.jdeb;
002
003import java.io.FileNotFoundException;
004
005public class ProducerFileNotFoundException extends FileNotFoundException {
006
007    private String filePath;
008
009    public ProducerFileNotFoundException() {
010        super();
011    }
012
013    public ProducerFileNotFoundException(String message) {
014        super(message);
015    }
016
017    public ProducerFileNotFoundException(String message, Throwable cause) {
018        super(message);
019        this.initCause(cause);
020    }
021
022    public void setFilePath(String path) {
023        this.filePath = path;
024    }
025
026    public String getFilePath() {
027        return this.filePath;
028    }
029}
